{"tid":1858284,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"工信部:中國口罩產能恢復六成","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:57:46.000Z","uid":104138,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"114633978165e5c5a718a6ca23a2b3a2bd6b7805","tid":1858284,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"工信部表示，目前中國口罩實際產能已恢復六成，日產量已經超過千萬隻，但口罩需求急增，供應仍存在短缺，1月24日到1月30日的7日內，共進口口罩逾5600萬隻。<br />\n<br />\n工信部亦稱，用於重症病房的醫務人員用的N95口罩，內地產能每日約60萬隻，並希望社會公眾盡量不要佔用該類口罩。<br />\n<br />\n中國為全球口罩生產最大國家，佔全球市佔率約50%，疫情未發生之時，中國口罩最高日產為2000多萬隻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2366267/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%A1%E9%83%A8%3A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2366267%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2583%25A8%253A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%25A2%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2590&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=160dc3ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2366267/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%A1%E9%83%A8%3A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90</a><br />\n<br />\n拎晒人地做生意既口罩先恢復六成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六成日產量已經超過千萬隻，當你一半人唔帶罩一日最少都要7億啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61977f50264c63a259ea85beb18140ce5b9c4ed","tid":1858284,"uid":63697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac